OL,5, Vernon Kay's BBC Radio 2 show has 6.9  
OL,6, million listeners, according to new    
OL,7, audience figures - 1.3 million fewer   
OL,8, than predecessor Ken Bruce pulled in   
OL,9, before he left the mid-morning slot.   
OL,11,FKay took over in May after Bruce left  
OL,12,Fthe BBC for Greatest Hits Radio.       
OL,14,FKay's ratings mean he has the most     
OL,15,Fpopular radio show in the UK.          
OL,17,FBut Bruce, going head-to-head with his 
OL,18,FRadio 2 successor, has increased the   
OL,19,Faudience for his new Greatest Hits show
OL,20,Fto 3.7 million, Rajar said.            
